Scores of the People Democratic Party (PDP) members including some of its executive members in Kazaure Local Government Area of Jigawa State have formally defected to the All Progressives Congress (APC) in Jigawa State. Speaking during their reception, Chairman of the LGA who is also an APC candidate for Kazaure/Roni/Yan kwashi/Gwiwa federal constituency, Arc. Muhammad Mukhtar Zanna expressed his happiness for having them in his party. PDP campaign to Tinubu: We’ll publish your corruption compendium PDP campaign to Tinubu: We’ll publish your corruption compendium Zanna noted that APC is a political party built upon national patriotism, love to humanity, justice, equality and selfless commitment. 